object_caption.name: Cabinet
object_caption.caption:
The image depicts a small, well-lit room with a gray carpeted floor. The room has a window on the left side, allowing natural light to enter. The window has horizontal blinds partially closed. 

On the right side of the room, there is a wooden cabinet with a light brown finish. The cabinet has three drawers, each with a horizontal handle. On top of the cabinet, there are a few items: a blue object, possibly a book or a folder, and a transparent plastic bag containing some items. 

Next to the cabinet, there is a wicker basket placed on the floor. The basket appears to be empty. 

In the foreground, there is a white, fluffy rug partially visible, suggesting that the room might be used for relaxation or as a waiting area. The walls of the room are painted in a light color, and the baseboards are black, creating a simple and clean aesthetic.
